									"Data": "根据以下 YAML 内容在 openshift-adp 项目中创建 DataProtectionApplication 对象。"
								}
							]
						},
						{
							"ID": "20221113113349-favunle",
							"Type": "NodeCodeBlock",
							"IsFencedCodeBlock": true,
